Rename Forecast and Hour

Forecast is now DailyForecast, Hour is HourlyForecast.

Both are now top level in WeatherReport, so you don't need to go
through a DailyForecast to get an Hourly one.

I'm now propagating the report time through to DailyForecasts and
Astronomy, so they've got the right timezone offset.

I've also finished (I think) adding javadoc to the data classes.
